name: Happy to Sad transformation
description:
Happy to Sad transformation
Part of depression Art
.
We cannot feel happy all the time, in this morphing animation show how we transform from happiness to sadness. First we feel happy, and put our smile face all the time. Then BOOOOOOMMMM !!!!. Some bad thing's happen and make us feel bad, and put our sadness crying face.
